ABOUT_US.missionStatement: Our mission is to provide care products to professionals and enthusiasts, making it easy for our customers to find the products they need to create beautiful and healthy nails
ABOUT_US.historyHTML:
Nail Essential is a family-owned business that has been providing high-quality nail care products to professionals and enthusiasts for over 20 years. It was founded in 2000 by Susan and John Smith, who saw a need for a reliable source of top-quality nail supplies for salons and spas in their area.

Starting from a small garage in their backyard, they began selling their products to local businesses and quickly gained a reputation for their exceptional customer service and high-quality products. As demand grew, they expanded their business and moved to a larger facility, allowing them to serve customers nationwide.

Over the years, Nail Essential has continued to prioritize quality and customer satisfaction, sourcing the best materials and working closely with manufacturers to ensure that their products meet the highest standards. Today, the company offers a wide selection of top-quality nail care products at competitive prices, along with exceptional customer service and support.

Despite its growth and success, Nail Essential remains committed to its roots as a family-owned business, and continues to operate with the same dedication to quality and customer service that Susan and John started with over 20 years ago.

CATEGORIES.name: Acrylic Nails
CATEGORIES.description: Find everything you need for stunning acrylic nails, including acrylic powders, liquids, and tools. Create beautiful and durable nail extensions with ease.

CATEGORIES.name: Nail Art

CATEGORIES.description: Browse our selection of professional nail tools, such as files, brushes, clippers, and cuticle pushers. Equip yourself with high-quality tools for the perfect manicure or pedicure.

PRODUCTS.name: Acrylic Nail Powder
PRODUCTS.intro: A professional-grade acrylic nail powder for strong nail extensions.
PRODUCTS.details: Our Acrylic Nail Powder creates durable and natural-looking nail extensions. The smooth, easy-to-apply formula ensures a flawless finish.

PRODUCTS.name: Acrylic Nail Brush
PRODUCTS.intro: A professional-quality acrylic nail brush for precise application.
PRODUCTS.details: Our Acrylic Nail Brush is designed for optimal control and precision during acrylic nail application. The high-quality bristles ensure smooth and even product distribution.

PRODUCTS.name: Nail Art Stickers
PRODUCTS.intro: A variety of nail art stickers for creative and unique nail designs.
PRODUCTS.details: Our Nail Art Stickers feature a wide range of designs, including floral, geometric, and abstract patterns. Easily enhance your manicure with these self-adhesive stickers.

PRODUCTS.name: Nail Art Glitter
PRODUCTS.intro: A set of dazzling nail art glitter for a touch of sparkle.
PRODUCTS.details: Our Nail Art Glitter comes in various colors and sizes, allowing you to create eye-catching and shimmery nail designs. Easily apply the glitter using your favorite top coat or nail glue.

PRODUCTS.name: Professional Nail File
PRODUCTS.intro: A dual-sided nail file for precise shaping and smoothing.
PRODUCTS.details: Our Professional Nail File features a medium grit side for shaping and a fine grit side for smoothing. The ergonomic design ensures comfortable and easy use.

PRODUCTS.name: Stainless Steel Cuticle Pusher
PRODUCTS.intro: A durable stainless steel cuticle pusher for professional results.
PRODUCTS.details: Our Stainless Steel Cuticle Pusher features a dual-ended design with a curved pusher for shaping and a pointed tip for cleaning under nails. The non-slip grip ensures precise control.

PRODUCTS.name: Precision Nail Clipper
PRODUCTS.intro: A high-quality nail clipper for clean and precise cuts.
PRODUCTS.details: Our Precision Nail Clipper features sharp blades and a comfortable grip for easy trimming. The built-in nail file allows for on-the-go touch-ups.

PRODUCTS.name: Nourishing Cuticle Oil
PRODUCTS.intro: A hydrating cuticle oil for healthy and strong nails.
PRODUCTS.details: Our Nourishing Cuticle Oil is formulated with natural oils and vitamins to moisturize and nourish cuticles, promoting healthy nail growth.

PRODUCTS.name: Nail Strengthener
PRODUCTS.intro: A fortifying nail strengthener for stronger, healthier nails.
PRODUCTS.details: Our Nail Strengthener is formulated with nourishing ingredients to help strengthen weak, brittle nails and improve overall nail health.

PRODUCTS.name: Gentle Nail Polish Remover
PRODUCTS.intro: A gentle yet effective nail polish remover for quick and easy removal.
PRODUCTS.details: Our Gentle Nail Polish Remover is formulated to quickly remove even the most stubborn nail polish without damaging your nails.

PRODUCTS.name: Mauve Nail Polish
PRODUCTS.intro: A stylish mauve nail polish for a sophisticated, trendy look.
PRODUCTS.details: Our Mauve Nail Polish features a long-lasting, chip-resistant formula. The rich color provides full coverage and smooth application.

PRODUCTS.name: Teal Nail Polish

PRODUCTS.details: Our Teal Nail Polish offers a long-lasting, chip-resistant finish. The high-pigment formula ensures full coverage and easy application.

PRODUCTS.name: Nude Nail Polish

PRODUCTS.details: Our Nude Nail Polish features a long-lasting, chip-resistant formula. The versatile color provides full coverage and smooth application.

PRODUCTS.name: Red Nail Polish

PRODUCTS.details: Our Red Nail Polish offers a long-lasting, chip-resistant finish. The rich, high-pigment formula ensures full coverage and easy application.

PRODUCTS.name: Quick Dry Top Coat

PRODUCTS.details: Our Quick Dry Top Coat seals in color and adds a high-gloss finish to your nails. The formula dries quickly to prevent smudges and prolong the life of your manicure.

PRODUCTS.details: Our Gel Base Coat provides a strong foundation for your gel polish, ensuring a smooth application and long-lasting wear.

PRODUCTS.name: Pink Gel Polish
PRODUCTS.intro: A beautiful pink gel polish for a long-lasting, shiny manicure.
PRODUCTS.details: Our Pink Gel Polish features a chip-resistant, high-gloss formula that lasts for weeks. The vibrant color provides full coverage and easy application.

PRODUCTS.name: Nail Stamping Kit
PRODUCTS.intro: A complete nail stamping kit for creating unique and intricate nail art.
PRODUCTS.details: Our Nail Stamping Kit includes a variety of stamping plates, a stamper, and a scraper. The plates feature intricate designs to help you create stunning nail art with ease.
